high_descs: Head around and turn left and turn right near the bed.

Turn right and walk towards the floorlamp.
Turn left and turn on the floorlamp.

high_descs: Turn left to head to the bedroom and walk to the bed on the right.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to walk to the floor lamp on the right.
Switch on the floorlamp and examine the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Examine the ladle under the floorlamp.
